      <title>南非商业信心增强 呼吁提高经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/south-africa-urged-to-lift-growth-as-business-confidence-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非商会表示，新成立的多党政府有机会促进经济增长和提振市场情绪，并宣布过去两个月企业信心略有回升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/south-africa-urged-to-lift-growth-as-business-confidence-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比亚东南部降雨量创纪录 引发新灾难担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/record-rainfall-in-southeast-libya-sparks-fear-of-new-disaster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[创纪录的降雨给利比亚东南部地区带来严重破坏，人们担心那里会再次发生类似去年造成数千人死亡和流离失所的洪水，因此利比亚的敌对政府联合起来为该地区居民提供援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/record-rainfall-in-southeast-libya-sparks-fear-of-new-disaster</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 09:10:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非和 B4SA 将重点关注能源、货运和监管修复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/south-africa-b4sa-to-focus-on-energy-freight-regulation-fixes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非政府和南非商业 — — 该机构正在帮助国家协调努力，解决国家崩溃的基础设施和治理问题 — — 计划在明年加速改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/south-africa-b4sa-to-focus-on-energy-freight-regulation-fixes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 09:07:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反移民骚乱逐渐平息 英国骚乱逮捕人数逾千人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/uk-riot-arrests-pass-1-000-as-anti-immigrant-disorder-subsides</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在首相基尔·斯塔默强调要加大惩罚力度以恢复平静之后，7 月底和本月初席卷英国的骚乱中被捕的人数已超过 1,000 人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/uk-riot-arrests-pass-1-000-as-anti-immigrant-disorder-subsides</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 08:57:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国法院裁定总理在道德案件中罪名成立，将其免职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thai-court-finds-pm-guilty-in-ethics-case-paving-way-for-ouster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国宪法法院裁定总理斯雷塔·塔维辛违反道德规范，解除其职务，这导致这个东南亚国家陷入新一轮的政治动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thai-court-finds-pm-guilty-in-ethics-case-paving-way-for-ouster</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 08:32:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯在最大规模空袭中击落 117 架无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/russia-shot-down-117-drones-in-one-of-largest-overnight-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是俄罗斯防空部队在战争期间最大规模的夜间袭击之一，共在各地区击落 117 架无人机和 4 枚战术导弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/russia-shot-down-117-drones-in-one-of-largest-overnight-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 05:19:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>被罢免的孟加拉国总理要求调查起义期间的死亡事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/ousted-bangladesh-pm-demands-probe-into-deaths-during-uprising</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国前总理谢赫·哈西娜呼吁对学生抗议活动中发生的死亡事件进行调查，这是她一周多前被赶下台以来首次正式发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/ousted-bangladesh-pm-demands-probe-into-deaths-during-uprising</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 05:08:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>岸田宣布退出后日本首相热门候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/top-contenders-for-japan-leadership-after-kishida-announces-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄周三表示，他不会参加 9 月份执政的自民党总裁选举，此后日本将迎来新领导人。由于自民党在议会中占据主导地位，自民党总裁几乎肯定会成为首相。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/top-contenders-for-japan-leadership-after-kishida-announces-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:12:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本首相岸田因支持率下降将下台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/japan-pm-kishida-won-t-run-for-party-leadership-race-kyodo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄不会在 9 月份竞选长期执政的自民党总裁第二任期，这为继任者首相的竞选铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/japan-pm-kishida-won-t-run-for-party-leadership-race-kyodo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 01:35:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
